6 4639 moveto (I recommend the following resolutions of core issues, these are seperable proposals:) show
6 4665 moveto (1\)  CV-Qualified return types:   Allow them.   Returns of class type handled symetrically with  
reference) show
6 4678 moveto (type returns for purpose of member selection, function overloading and explicit binding to  
references.) show
6 4691 moveto (Note that these are similar to lvalues, but not exactly see #1,#2, #4, and #5 in first section.   
